@6patera9

These mods definitely are not going to work on a server, I believe EE and BTW don't have any functioning versions, and the other mods are the single player only versions included.

I believe there are versions of buildcraft that are multiplayer though, but not in this pack.

@6patera9,

This pack definitely won't work with a server.

There are parts (buildcraft I think) that have versions that will work, but BTW and EE definitely cannot work with any server software.

@raven49,

Neither Mo' Creatures and Creeps nor Weirdoes  use MC Forge, which is a requirement for them to all *easily* mesh together.

I wouldn't be surprised if getting these two mods alone to work wouldn't be possible due to how much they change that's similar though.  If it is possible it would be quite complicated and wouldn't work with the rest of these mods.  If they start using MC Forge I would put it in a pack though.
